               <p>I was at the <placeName id="t17780429-61-crimeloc288">Castle and Falcon Inn, Aldersgate-street</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17780429-61-crimeloc288" type="placeName" value="Castle and Falcon Inn, Aldersgate-street"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t17780429-61-crimeloc288" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17780429-61-off286 t17780429-61-crimeloc288"></join>. I saw the prisoner going out at the gateway with a parcel under his coat. I hallooed out to him, You rascal! what have<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="177804290047"></xptr> you got there? and he dropped the parcel and ran away. I alarmed the people of the inn, and he was pursued and taken.</p>

               <p>[
               <persName id="t17780429-61-person566">
